{"tid":138371,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"新車 mazda 6 vs BMW 320i GT","createTime":"2017-02-28T13:46:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-01T04:24:55.000Z","uid":8495,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2369d512aa3ae51adcc1e4d5fdba0cb09d035aa1","tid":138371,"uid":8495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T13:46:53.000Z","msg":"小弟24 歲，呢兩部車都做緊promotion, 兩部都16年製，想問下巴絲們意見<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMazda 6 2.5 R-Grade<br />\n車價 260k<br />\n隻soul red 好靚，外型又sporty, 配19吋合金鈴，音響好。但缺點係FF 同鋼水差（？）<br />\n<br />\nBMW 320i GT Executive<br />\n車價 400k<br />\n歐洲車，鋼水好，外型都ok 型又高貴d, FR, 但得17吋鈴，同埋聽人講玩bmw 唔上直6 好似好笨柒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢部係我第二部車，岩岩操完車順利畢業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n假日車，比著巴打們會點揀？"},{"pid":"ed97c332ee67201f2aaab9ed4450d991864a5c5a","tid":138371,"uid":20336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T13:50:43.000Z","msg":"叻仔 wow, 24 歲有本事考慮拎 40k 出架假日車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73397a2f3f321e9d76e53412318581852a900653","tid":138371,"uid":20336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T13:51:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叻仔 wow, 24 歲有本事考慮拎 <span style=\"color: red;\">400k</span> 出架假日車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"2c34e6931c1bbf6ce4b72d9bdf94604cd6b70b00","tid":138371,"uid":8495,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T13:55:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>叻仔 wow, 24 歲有本事考慮拎 <span style=\"color: red;\">400k</span> 出架假日車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n你當我兩部都買得起，唔係靠屋企，唔係想show off 只係無人問<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 幫下我啦巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"611efd9fd021927f92708d65be05eef617d02aec","tid":138371,"uid":22585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T14:12:26.000Z","msg":"響連登車台講鋼水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a226ec3b53edcd26275621ab99075bd778511971","tid":138371,"uid":8495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T14:19:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>響連登車台講鋼水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  , 上左車台無耐，一直無留意開<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24167e59ce64e1875c9fe625656e37ee0b012f8b","tid":138371,"uid":31809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:48:39.000Z","msg":"一定係 Mazda 6 Diesel R Grade<br />\n絕版柴油完勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鋼水唔使擔心<br />\n萬事得新車用好多高拉力鋼"},{"pid":"feb0f6ec4ce072c451d4d99a693755d93a6f0d42","tid":138371,"uid":29423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:59:45.000Z","msg":"上連登一定個個推mazda6"},{"pid":"58dc7dad3ab86c3186a9db2c8b86e907558ac936","tid":138371,"uid":52591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T16:06:51.000Z","msg":"40k 頂配ma6 完勝 入門無option 320"},{"pid":"907ce18d61f8041c86b387285bd30b868e885fd1","tid":138371,"uid":41642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"